# Morse Code Reader

[MorseCodeReader.com](https://morsecodereader.com) – A free online Morse Code Translator.  
Easily convert text to Morse code and decode Morse signals back into plain text.

## 🚀 Features
- Text to Morse code converter
- Morse code to text decoder
- Supports international Morse code standards
- Simple, fast, and mobile-friendly

## 🌐 Live Website
👉 [https://morsecodereader.com](https://morsecodereader.com)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

